{"id":"XIAOTIANE7","scripts":[{"stopbgm":true,"mode":1,"sequence":[["春風の十字星\n\n<size=45>その七  事件解決！<\/size>",1]]},{"bgName":"bg_story_school","dir":1,"say":"アークロイヤルさん、すみません。うち、勝手に容疑者だと疑ってしまって……","nameColor":"#a9f548","bgm":"story-1","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":201080,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"bgName":"bg_story_school","dir":1,"say":"ぼくも最初そう思ってた……ごめん……","nameColor":"#a9f548","side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"paintingFadeOut":{"side":0,"time":0.5},"actor":201110,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"bgName":"bg_story_school","side":0,"dir":-1,"say":"で、でもアークロイヤルさんの普段の行いの結果でしょう？ま、まあ…ひとまず謝るわよ……すみませんでした……","actor":201090,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"bgName":"bg_story_school","side":1,"dir":1,"say":"（まったく、駆逐艦の妹たちが謝る姿…最高だぜ！）う、うふぉ！？","actor":207020,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"bgName":"bg_story_school","side":0,"dir":-1,"say":"もう、アークロイヤルはすぐこれだから誤解されるんじゃないの？","actor":201230,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"bgName":"bg_story_school","side":0,"dir":1,"say":"と、とにかく服を見つけられてよかったぁ……アークロイヤルさん、服をうちに返してください…この格好すっごく恥ずかしいよぉ……","actor":201101,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"bgName":"bg_story_school","side":1,"dir":1,"say":"（ハッ…！シグニットちゃんの水着姿に見とれて服を返すの忘れてた）も、もちろんだとも！","actor":207020,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"bgName":"bg_story_school","side":0,"dir":1,"say":"でもこの水着、やっぱりシグニットに似合うね。うちもシグニットほどじゃなくていいから、スタイル良かったらなぁ…はぁ……","actor":201080,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"bgName":"bg_story_school","side":1,"dir":1,"say":"ふん！私は別にうらやま…羨ましくないの！","actor":201090,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"bgName":"bg_story_school","side":0,"dir":-1,"say":"シグニットのここってある意味凄いじゃない？確かに暴力的だわ。","actor":201230,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"bgName":"bg_story_school","side":1,"dir":1,"say":"？？？どこが「ボウリョクテキ」なの？","actor":201110,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"bgName":"bg_story_school","side":1,"dir":1,"say":"ある意味ね…ヴァンパイアも結構凄いのにね…","actor":201090,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"bgName":"bg_story_school","side":2,"dir":1,"say":"ふぇ…うち褒められてるってことなのぉ…？","actor":201101,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"bgName":"bg_story_school","side":2,"dir":1,"say":"みんな服探しを手伝ってくれてありがとう…うぅぅ…","actor":201101,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"bgName":"bg_story_school","dir":1,"say":"ああ！服も無事に見つかって結果オーライだ！かなり探し回ったようだし、そろそろご飯でも食べにいかないか？せっかくだからこの私がおごってもいいぞ？","nameColor":"#a9f548","side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"paintingFadeOut":{"side":1,"time":0.5},"actor":207020,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"bgName":"bg_story_school","dir":1,"withoutPainting":true,"say":"おお！","nameColor":"#a9f548","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actorName":"みんな","actor":0,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"bgName":"bg_story_school","side":2,"dir":1,"say":"ご、ご飯！…もいいけど、まずは服を着替えさせて――！","actor":201101,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"bgName":"bg_story_school","dir":1,"say":"ぐへっ、駆逐艦の妹たちと一緒にご飯を食べられるぞ…！（もちろんだ！先に着替えてきてくれ！）","nameColor":"#a9f548","side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"paintingFadeOut":{"side":0,"time":0.5},"actor":207020,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"bgName":"bg_story_school","dir":1,"withoutPainting":true,"say"